text: Ali Hussein (born on 1 January 1953) is a former Iraqi football striker who played for Iraq in the 1976 AFC Asian Cup qualification. He played for the national team between 1975 and 1981. Ali Hussein was topscorer of the Iraqi League in 1979-80 and in 1983-84.\- RSSSF ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Iraq international footballers Category:Al-Shorta SC players Category:Living people Category:Association football forwards
